类 RXObserver

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.rfid.rxobserver.RXObserver
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    java.util.Observer

    public class RXObserver
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.Observer
    The implementation of #Observer.You can override the according method and register it to #RFIDReaderHelper. Then you can get the data you will.

      • onExeCMDStatus

        protected void onExeCMDStatus(byte cmd,
                              byte status)
        This method will callback when the command you send only carries command execution status code no extra data, or the command return exception data.
        参数:
        cmd - The execution command reference CMD
        status - The execution status of command,reference ERROR.

      • onInventoryTag

        protected void onInventoryTag(RXInventoryTag tag)
        This method will callback when you send inventory command RFIDReaderHelper.realTimeInventory(byte, byte), RFIDReaderHelper.getInventoryBuffer(byte),RFIDReaderHelper.customizedSessionTargetInventory(byte, byte, byte, byte) ,RFIDReaderHelper.fastSwitchAntInventory(byte, byte, byte, byte, byte, byte, byte, byte, byte, byte, byte) or enable the trigger. Return inventoried tag it will be wrapped RXInventoryTag object.
        参数:
        tag - The RXInventoryTag object contain tag information.

      • onLock6BTag

        protected void onLock6BTag(byte nAntID,
                           byte nStatus)
        This method will callback when you send RFIDReaderHelper.iso180006BLockTag(byte, byte[], byte) command.
        参数:
        nAntID - current antenna id.
        nStatus - Lock 6B return status (0x00:The byte is successfully locked. 0xFE:The byte is already locked. 0xFF:The byte cant be locked)

      • onLockQuery6BTag

        protected void onLockQuery6BTag(byte nAntID,
                                byte nStatus)
        This method will callback when you send RFIDReaderHelper.iso180006BQueryLockTag(byte, byte[], byte) command.
        参数:
        nAntID - current antenna id.
        nStatus - Lock 6B return status (0x00:The byte is not locked.. 0xFE:The byte is locked.)
